{"tid":836672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮狂奔險仆搵Baby集郵","createTime":"2018-09-25T22:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T17:39:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4fe6399295df20887953683c6aada500977aa6d","tid":836672,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T22:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Hl_4n1rY.jbW3EvnQYJJhg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/dcd26a9a6412e15c5238e08d72151552\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHl_4n1rY.jbW3EvnQYJJhg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fdcd26a9a6412e15c5238e08d72151552&h=465e5047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S4jtBMLf1MhX1QL6Me9t0A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/ede84b54cd03e989e4429c2f0936efb1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FS4jtBMLf1MhX1QL6Me9t0A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fede84b54cd03e989e4429c2f0936efb1&h=44d01f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ganMHFSVhrcbDUOs8OXYYQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/43dcc54eb702b7084e8a9b73dd77c935\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FganMHFSVhrcbDUOs8OXYYQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F43dcc54eb702b7084e8a9b73dd77c935&h=2a822d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ybffWEy9poSvQ0G83YJnfg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/6a1841427db4b5201780175209e15aee\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FybffWEy9poSvQ0G83YJnfg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F6a1841427db4b5201780175209e15aee&h=414f2db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊三房千金何超蓮近日「處女下海」，首次獲邀出席巴黎時裝周，以民族風出戰，與女神楊穎（Angelababy）合照留念，兩位美女同框，美不勝收。<br />\n<br />\n向來對時尚甚有觸覺的超蓮，近日獲邀首次出席巴黎時裝周，為隆重其事，她以一身民族風造型，配襯波鞋亮相，另外又以高貴打扮配襯高踭鞋示人，展現不同的形象。超蓮大呻當地交通繁忙，往會場途中遇上塞車：「中間要落車跑去會場，唔係好慣着高踭鞋搞到跌吓跌吓咁！」到達會場後，超蓮見到藝人Angelababy、韓星孔孝真等，即變身小粉絲，分別向她們「集郵」留念，又大讚兩人好靚。<br />\n<br />\n溫碧霞晒仙氣<br />\n期間，超蓮與Baby言談甚歡，她說：「Angelababy話佢翌日就要離開飛到倫敦工作，而我就會睇晒成個Fashion Week先走。」問到首次去時裝周睇騷有何感受？她說：「好震撼，嚟到睇咗第一個品牌騷，現場好靚、好大，搭咗個好大嘅帳篷，台中心有人跳舞，喺後台我仲同設計師Maria Grazia Chiuri傾偈同合照。」<br />\n<br />\n至於藝人溫碧霞亦有份睇騷，穿上吊帶長裙盡顯仙氣，並指完騷後會在當地逗留多兩日，順道拍攝寫真集；內地女星王子文更以奇怪妝容搶鏡，成為另類焦點。<br />\n<br />\n蔡依林變「大媽」<br />\n至於另一品牌時裝騷中，台灣天后蔡依林以「大媽Look」示人，與型男余文樂齊齊睇騷，成為焦點，二人更Chok爆大擺甫士合照，十分老友。"},{"pid":"062997116f9c9331852069a15fda022769c29dba","tid":836672,"uid":118758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:17:32.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超蓮"},{"pid":"238877644bd9d61e06f0298224a9e40394cd2aeb","tid":836672,"uid":37431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:27:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯「狂撞臉」<br />\n<br />\n再睇第一張相，咁似嘅 同一個醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f57e5a2c54e1dd6eed222c50f2a3740da2cfda0","tid":836672,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d62d1a024d92f3aafa8a344d95defa013a99d6d","tid":836672,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid